1
00:00:26,467 --> 00:00:27,567
Who is it?

2
00:00:35,233 --> 00:00:37,200
Can I... help you?

3
00:00:41,333 --> 00:00:42,533
Mr. Heo Dong Hwa?

4
00:00:43,133 --> 00:00:44,167
Yes, that's me.

5
00:00:45,067 --> 00:00:46,467
Can I help you?

6
00:02:06,500 --> 00:02:08,333
Yes, I'm about to handle it now.

7
00:02:08,333 --> 00:02:10,933
<i>Stop. Abort the operation.</i>

8
00:02:10,933 --> 00:02:12,067
Huh?

9
00:02:12,067 --> 00:02:14,567
<i>Heo Dong Hwa has a phone containing evidence.</i>

10
00:02:15,833 --> 00:02:18,267
<i>The mayor ordered us to retrieve that phone.</i>

11
00:02:20,033 --> 00:02:21,367
Then...

12
00:02:21,367 --> 00:02:24,167
<i>They say he hid the phone
somewhere in his house.</i>

13
00:02:25,300 --> 00:02:26,733
Should I wait?

14
00:02:26,733 --> 00:02:28,400
<i>Find the item first.</i>

15
00:02:28,400 --> 00:02:30,167
<i>Until then, don't kill Heo Dong Hwa.</i>

16
00:02:40,633 --> 00:02:43,400
<i>There should be a secret passage
leading to the basement of the house.</i>

17
00:02:43,400 --> 00:02:45,000
<i>Lock up Heo Dong Hwa there.</i>

18
00:03:20,600 --> 00:03:23,533
<i>It's a secluded place,
so no one should be coming.</i>

19
00:03:23,533 --> 00:03:26,233
<i>But be careful not to be seen by anyone.</i>

20
00:03:27,967 --> 00:03:30,700
<i>But have you given some thought
to what I mentioned last time?</i>

21
00:03:33,100 --> 00:03:36,133
<i>This doesn't seem like the right time
to bring that up.</i>

22
00:03:36,933 --> 00:03:38,600
<i>Don't you know how important this task is?</i>

23
00:03:40,433 --> 00:03:42,500
<i>Then when can I get an answer?</i>

24
00:03:46,567 --> 00:03:48,400
<i>Take care of this task flawlessly first.</i>

25
00:03:53,100 --> 00:03:56,400
<i>Then we'll meet in person and talk.</i>

26
00:04:01,133 --> 00:04:03,867
<i>Okay, I'll see you soon.</i>

27
00:05:07,533 --> 00:05:09,700
Dong Hwa, I'm home.

28
00:05:09,700 --> 00:05:11,333
Are you in there?

29
00:05:11,333 --> 00:05:12,833
I'm coming in.

30
00:05:15,667 --> 00:05:16,767
Heo Dong Hwa.

31
00:05:19,500 --> 00:05:20,833
Who are you?

32
00:05:24,833 --> 00:05:25,967
Don't tell me...

33
00:05:31,300 --> 00:05:32,400
Are you Dong Jin?

34
00:05:34,700 --> 00:05:35,767
No?

35
00:05:36,467 --> 00:05:37,800
You're Dong Jin, right?

36
00:05:39,667 --> 00:05:42,900
- Who...
- I'm Tae Jeong, Dong Hwa's friend.

37
00:05:44,267 --> 00:05:45,667
Don't you remember me?

38
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:49,100
Tae Jeong?

39
00:05:49,100 --> 00:05:51,800
Dong Jin, it's been so long, you know?

40
00:05:51,800 --> 00:05:53,833
Has it been 10 years
since you went to the States?

41
00:05:53,833 --> 00:05:56,967
No, it must be more like 15 years, right?

42
00:06:01,333 --> 00:06:04,300
It was really hard getting here.

43
00:06:08,367 --> 00:06:09,733
Did you come here alone?

44
00:06:10,400 --> 00:06:12,233
Walked all the way without a car?

45
00:06:12,233 --> 00:06:15,900
Yes, I took the bus and got off,
and then walked from there.

46
00:06:19,900 --> 00:06:21,833
By the way, when is Dong Hwa coming back?

47
00:06:24,667 --> 00:06:27,667
Didn't Dong Hwa tell you I was coming?

48
00:06:29,267 --> 00:06:32,200
No, he didn't tell me anything.

49
00:06:32,200 --> 00:06:34,567
I got a job in Dongcheon.

50
00:06:34,567 --> 00:06:37,700
There's a problem with the company dorm,
so I can't move in for about a week.

51
00:06:37,700 --> 00:06:40,467
I talked to Dong Hwa,
and he said I could stay here.

52
00:06:40,467 --> 00:06:42,800
That's an arrangement
between you and Heo Dong Hwa, isn't it?

53
00:06:42,800 --> 00:06:44,867
It doesn't seem to have
anything to do with me.

54
00:06:49,867 --> 00:06:52,133
I'll just wait quietly here.

55
00:06:52,133 --> 00:06:55,000
Since we agreed to meet here,
I should just wait for him.

56
00:06:56,633 --> 00:06:59,867
By the way, Dong Jin,
you really don't remember me?

57
00:06:59,867 --> 00:07:01,467
We were quite close.

58
00:07:05,333 --> 00:07:07,633
Is it because we were too little?

59
00:07:07,633 --> 00:07:10,733
Actually, if I saw you on the street,
I probably wouldn't recognize you either.

60
00:07:14,900 --> 00:07:16,800
Is it okay if I sleep on the sofa?

61
00:07:16,800 --> 00:07:19,300
Dong Hwa said it's okay
for me to stay in the living room.

62
00:07:19,300 --> 00:07:20,367
No.

63
00:07:20,367 --> 00:07:23,000
As I said, the arrangement between you
and Heo Dong Hwa has nothing to do with me--

64
00:07:23,000 --> 00:07:24,367
It will get dark soon, won't it?

65
00:07:25,333 --> 00:07:27,533
What if I go out and meet someone strange?

66
00:07:28,367 --> 00:07:31,433
I even talked to him this morning,
so he should reply soon.

67
00:07:32,633 --> 00:07:34,667
But where did he go?

68
00:07:56,033 --> 00:07:58,167
<i>An unexpected situation has arisen.</i>

69
00:07:59,967 --> 00:08:03,900
<i>A person named Chu Tae Jeong
showed up at the house out of nowhere.</i>

70
00:08:05,067 --> 00:08:07,667
<i>He seems to be an old friend of Heo Dong Hwa.</i>

71
00:08:07,667 --> 00:08:11,233
<i>He mistakenly thinks I'm Heo Dong Jin,
Heo Dong Hwa's old brother.</i>

72
00:08:12,333 --> 00:08:15,033
<i>It's going to be difficult to proceed
according to the plan.</i>

73
00:08:17,133 --> 00:08:18,967
<i>Since my face has been exposed,</i>

74
00:08:20,300 --> 00:08:22,333
<i>I'll temporarily suspend the operation.</i>

75
00:08:23,567 --> 00:08:26,533
I'll get rid of him first thing tomorrow.

76
00:08:26,533 --> 00:08:27,800
Dong Jin.

77
00:08:31,300 --> 00:08:32,300
Don't you know how to knock?

78
00:08:32,300 --> 00:08:34,033
Oh, right. I should've knocked.

79
00:08:35,667 --> 00:08:37,200
May I come in?

80
00:08:37,933 --> 00:08:39,833
- For what?
- Well...

81
00:08:41,033 --> 00:08:45,400
Dong Hwa said
he'd leave a blanket for me to use.

82
00:08:46,000 --> 00:08:47,533
I was wondering if you knew where it is.

83
00:08:52,533 --> 00:08:55,767
- I don't know.
- Then, may I look for it?

84
00:08:55,767 --> 00:08:57,433
It wasn't in the living room.

85
00:08:59,433 --> 00:09:00,500
Wait.

86
00:09:01,800 --> 00:09:03,167
I'll look for it.

87
00:09:03,167 --> 00:09:04,433
What?

88
00:09:07,500 --> 00:09:09,267
Is this your room, Dong Jin?

89
00:09:11,500 --> 00:09:13,133
Where does Dong Hwa sleep?

90
00:09:15,000 --> 00:09:16,167
What?

91
00:09:16,167 --> 00:09:19,533
It seems like this house
only has one bedroom.

92
00:09:19,533 --> 00:09:22,700
Oh, Dong Hwa sleeps in the living room.

93
00:09:26,267 --> 00:09:28,533
You don't think
anything happened to him, right?

94
00:09:28,533 --> 00:09:30,133
I still haven't heard from him.

95
00:09:30,733 --> 00:09:32,300
Maybe something urgent come up.

96
00:09:36,267 --> 00:09:37,267
It's not in here either.

97
00:09:39,867 --> 00:09:45,633
Just... use this to sleep.

98
00:09:46,967 --> 00:09:48,133
What about you?

99
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:50,600
It's okay. I'm fine.

100
00:11:24,667 --> 00:11:26,100
Do you want to play catch?

101
00:11:27,933 --> 00:11:29,567
I'm having trouble sleeping.

102
00:11:32,733 --> 00:11:34,833
What does that have to do with playing catch?

103
00:11:36,333 --> 00:11:40,333
Moving around and sweating
might help me fall asleep.

104
00:11:44,567 --> 00:11:48,533
This is the signed ball I gave you as a gift.

105
00:11:53,733 --> 00:11:55,567
Back in elementary school in Jamsil.

106
00:11:57,433 --> 00:11:58,833
Don't you remember?

107
00:11:59,467 --> 00:12:00,667
It's the home run ball.

108
00:12:02,700 --> 00:12:05,133
I gave it to you before you left as a gift.

109
00:12:06,500 --> 00:12:08,033
I know.

110
00:12:08,633 --> 00:12:10,233
The ball signed by Lee Dae Ho.

111
00:12:11,933 --> 00:12:13,467
Of course, I remember.

112
00:12:15,300 --> 00:12:17,200
But it's not Lee Dae Ho.

113
00:12:17,200 --> 00:12:18,600
It's Lee Dae Hyung.

114
00:12:20,333 --> 00:12:23,133
Don't you know how rare
a Lee Dae Hyung's home run ball is?

115
00:12:23,133 --> 00:12:24,467
I'm disappointed.

116
00:12:25,067 --> 00:12:26,800
Are you really Dong Jin?

117
00:12:32,067 --> 00:12:33,467
Okay, fine.

118
00:12:46,667 --> 00:12:51,067
By the way, Dong Jin,
you seem to have become really quiet.

119
00:12:51,800 --> 00:12:52,867
Is that so?

120
00:12:53,700 --> 00:12:55,833
But I like quiet people.

121
00:12:56,448 --> 00:12:59,733
Since I'm more the talkative type.

122
00:12:59,733 --> 00:13:03,900
Yeah, I'm more comfortable listening too.

123
00:13:07,800 --> 00:13:11,000
But Dong Jin, did you
come back from the US for good?

124
00:13:13,900 --> 00:13:15,367
Yes.

125
00:13:15,367 --> 00:13:16,833
That's good.

126
00:13:19,367 --> 00:13:22,967
I was really upset
when you suddenly left like that.

127
00:13:25,667 --> 00:13:28,833
Actually, I gave you that signed ball
because I wanted to be friends with you.

128
00:13:38,500 --> 00:13:39,933
Let's hang out more.

129
00:13:45,700 --> 00:13:46,800
Okay.

130
00:13:54,600 --> 00:13:57,067
By the way, when did you come back to Korea?

131
00:13:57,067 --> 00:13:58,533
Dong Hwa didn't say anything.

132
00:14:02,467 --> 00:14:05,633
Well... It was not long ago.

133
00:14:06,700 --> 00:14:08,133
Why did you come back?

134
00:14:14,867 --> 00:14:16,433
I wanted to start fresh.

135
00:14:25,833 --> 00:14:27,067
Welcome back.

136
00:14:33,633 --> 00:14:37,067
Dong Jin, it seems like
you're getting your old skills back.

137
00:14:37,067 --> 00:14:38,700
I'll throw it properly too.

138
00:14:45,400 --> 00:14:46,967
You call that a proper throw?

139
00:14:57,567 --> 00:14:58,567
Are you okay?

140
00:15:02,200 --> 00:15:03,833
I think I broke my bone.

141
00:15:04,667 --> 00:15:06,733
I'll get some ice.

142
00:15:06,733 --> 00:15:07,733
Dong Jin!

143
00:15:11,667 --> 00:15:13,300
You're still so gullible.

144
00:15:14,233 --> 00:15:15,667
I'll go wash up first.

145
00:15:49,933 --> 00:15:50,967
Sorry.

146
00:16:19,333 --> 00:16:20,600
<i>Got your message.</i>

147
00:16:21,633 --> 00:16:22,900
<i>Someone came by?</i>

148
00:16:23,667 --> 00:16:24,700
Yes.

149
00:16:25,433 --> 00:16:27,333
As I said earlier,
I'll send him away tomorrow...

150
00:16:27,333 --> 00:16:28,667
<i>Kill him tonight.</i>

151
00:16:30,500 --> 00:16:32,067
Pardon me?

152
00:16:32,067 --> 00:16:34,033
<i>Who told you to stop the operation?</i>

153
00:16:34,933 --> 00:16:36,633
<i>You don't have that authority.</i>

154
00:16:38,167 --> 00:16:40,067
<i>Just do what you're told.</i>

155
00:18:14,267 --> 00:18:15,633
Oh, Dong Jin!

156
00:18:22,400 --> 00:18:23,967
Can't you keep it down a little?

157
00:18:24,967 --> 00:18:25,967
Sorry.

158
00:18:27,200 --> 00:18:28,967
But can't I just listen to this one song?

159
00:18:32,967 --> 00:18:33,967
Shut it.

160
00:18:36,567 --> 00:18:37,600
Okay.

161
00:18:40,267 --> 00:18:41,267
Go inside.

162
00:18:42,300 --> 00:18:43,433
Sleep in the bed.

163
00:18:44,033 --> 00:18:45,133
Huh?

164
00:18:45,133 --> 00:18:46,500
The sofa is uncomfortable.

165
00:18:46,500 --> 00:18:49,433
No, the owner should sleep in the bed.

166
00:18:49,433 --> 00:18:51,600
I can sleep anywhere
as long as I lay my head down.

167
00:18:53,200 --> 00:18:57,433
But in the living room,
it will be hard to fall into a deep sleep.

168
00:18:58,700 --> 00:19:00,633
I'm really fine.

169
00:19:03,367 --> 00:19:06,067
But if that's what you prefer,
I'll do as you say.

170
00:19:11,733 --> 00:19:12,733
Dong Jin!

171
00:19:14,400 --> 00:19:15,667
Good night.

172
00:19:35,133 --> 00:19:36,767
<i>Why aren't you replying?</i>

173
00:19:39,300 --> 00:19:41,267
<i>I'm with Dong Jin.</i>

174
00:19:42,933 --> 00:19:44,433
<i>But Dong Jin...</i>

175
00:19:45,767 --> 00:19:48,400
As I said, the arrangement between you
and Heo Dong Hwa has nothing to do with me--

176
00:19:48,400 --> 00:19:49,633
It will get dark soon, won't it?

177
00:19:50,833 --> 00:19:52,867
What if I go out and meet someone strange?

178
00:19:54,233 --> 00:19:55,233
Use this to sleep.

179
00:19:56,800 --> 00:19:57,800
What about you?

180
00:19:58,867 --> 00:20:00,267
It's okay. I'm fine.

181
00:20:01,367 --> 00:20:02,967
You're still so gullible.

182
00:20:10,700 --> 00:20:12,167
<i>Why is he so cute?</i>

183
00:20:12,800 --> 00:20:14,200
<i>It makes me want to tease him.</i>

184
00:20:15,067 --> 00:20:16,700
<i>I almost felt a little flutter...</i>

185
00:20:16,700 --> 00:20:18,600
[I almost felt a little flutter...]

186
00:20:30,300 --> 00:20:31,333
What's this?

187
00:20:32,833 --> 00:20:34,267
Is this Dong Jin's?

188
00:22:02,067 --> 00:22:03,067
Hey, Heo Dong Hwa.

189
00:22:04,700 --> 00:22:06,067
You know Chu Tae Jeong, don't you?

190
00:22:07,500 --> 00:22:08,667
Chu Tae Jeong?

191
00:22:11,400 --> 00:22:12,867
Tae Jeong is here?

192
00:22:15,800 --> 00:22:17,433
Answer the question.

193
00:22:18,533 --> 00:22:20,700
He's my oldest friend.

194
00:22:24,367 --> 00:22:25,633
What does he do?

195
00:22:33,167 --> 00:22:35,733
[Chu Tae Jeong]

196
00:22:35,733 --> 00:22:37,467
Tae Jeong is a cop.

197
00:22:42,267 --> 00:22:44,667
You can never escape him.

